#: ../../source/how_to/index.rst:4
msgid "How-To Recipes"
msgstr "如何做(How-To)"

#: ../../source/how_to/index.rst:6
msgid ""
"Short, focused answers to common \"I want to do X\" questions. Each "
"recipe is self-contained: problem statement, code or CSV edit, expected "
"result. They assume you've worked through :doc:`../Quickstart` once and "
"know how to run a solve."
msgstr ""
"针对常见的 \"我想做 X\" 类问题给出简短、聚焦的解答。每个秘籍自包含:问题描述、代码或 CSV 修改、预期结果。前提是你已完成一次 "
":doc:`../Quickstart`,知道如何运行求解。"

